"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","abstract":[{"text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}]},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]}}}